paragraphs.body: McAfee was nominated for two Young Artist Awards, the first for "Best Youth Actor in a Voice-over Role - TV or Movie" for his work in the 1992 film Batman, followed by one for "Best Youth Actor Leading Role in a Television Series" for his work in the 1993 film Home Free.
